### -------------------- CONFIG TESTS --------------------

### Criar Config
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/configs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "projectId": 4,
  "llmCredentialsId": {{llmCredentialId}},
  "modelName": "phi3:latest",
  "maxIter": 6,
  "checkPointInterval": 3,
  "additionalParams": {
    "llm.api_base": "{{ollamaDockerBase}}",
    "llm.temperature": "0.7",
    "database.population_size": "20",
    "database.num_islands": "1",
    "evaluator.parallel_evaluations": "1",
    "llm.timeout": "180",
    "llm.retries": "1",
    "llm.max_tokens": "256",
    "prompt.num_top_programs": "1",
    "prompt.num_diverse_programs": "1",
    "evaluator.cascade_evaluation": "false"
  }
}

### Ler Config por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/configs/{{configId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

